            <div class="col-lg-2">
                <div class=" d-flex justify-content-center p-3">
                    <img class="w-h-140px rounded-circle" src="../img/esg/esg-social-networking.svg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="text-center m-2">
                    <h3 class="h3-title-color">善用社群的力量</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center m-3 mt-4">
                    <h5>
                        我淨灘。我驕傲。
                        讓淨灘成為新時尚
                    </h5>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-2">
                <div class=" d-flex justify-content-center p-3">
                    <img class="w-h-140px rounded-circle" src="../img/esg/esg-creation.svg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="text-center m-2">
                    <h3 class="h3-title-color">遊戲化的集體創作</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center m-3 mt-4">
                    <h5>提高全民參與度並增強影響力</h5>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-2">
                <div class=" d-flex justify-content-center p-3">
                    <img class="w-h-140px rounded-circle" src="../img/esg/esg-immediate.svg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="text-center m-2">
                    <h3 class="h3-title-color">即 時 行 『垃』</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center m-3 mt-4">
                    <h5>
                        不用等待活動發起——
                        讓遊客. 居民隨時參與淨灘
                    </h5>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-2">
                <div class=" d-flex justify-content-center p-3">
                    <img class="w-h-140px rounded-circle" src="../img/esg/esg-Incentives.svg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="text-center m-2">
                    <h3 class="h3-title-color">擴大誘因、提高參加意願</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center m-3 mt-4">
                    <h5>
                        異業結盟Win-Win
